comment: Rose (CHI) makes incidental contact with Williams (CHA) that does not affect his RSBQ on the play to the basket.
Walker (CHA) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Rose (CHI) that does not affect his RSBQ on the driving shot attempt.
Jefferson (CHA) sets the screen on Snell (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Butler (CHI) makes incidental contact with Batum (CHA) as both players attempt to secure the loose ball.
